	(text "This module acts as a GPIB/HP-IB (General Purpose Interface Bus) controller that reads and sends \ncommands to a PM2812 power supply.The USB-C port on the board allows serial communication with a \ncomputer to monitor the power supply. Additionally, an RS485 interface is exposed for a desk-\nmounted control panel which will display power supply status and allow for control."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 25.4 53.34 0)
		(effects
